<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM4.5">
<l>kampamata yāṉaik kaḻuttakattiṉ mēliruntu</l>
<l>iṉpamaruñ celvamu mivvaracum yāṉvēṇṭēṉ</l>
<l>emperumā ṉīca ṉeḻilvēṅ kaṭamalaimēl</l>
<l>tampakamāy niṟkun tavamuṭaiyē ṉāvēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I shall not desire this kingdom or the happiness-abiding wealth</l>
<l rend="indent">[that is] sitting upon the neck of an elephant in must that trembles.</l>
<l>I shall possess the [fruit of] tapas [that enables me] to stand as a clump of grass</l>
<l rend="indent">upon the mountain of the beautiful Veṅkaṭa of the Supreme Being, our Lord.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
